# DEPRECATED - Migrated from Vercel to Cloudflare Pages (2026-06)
#
# Cloudflare Pages automatically handles SPA rewrites (fallback to index.html)
# and has excellent default caching for /assets/* and PWA files.
#
# No vercel.json equivalent needed. Configure in Cloudflare dashboard:
# - Build command: cd frontend && npm ci && npm run build
# - Output: frontend/dist
# - Env var: VITE_API_URL
#
# Headers for PWA can be set in Cloudflare Pages → Custom Pages Rules if needed.
